{"tid":1667301,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍現況","createTime":"2019-10-21T11:26:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T12:15:32.000Z","uid":127333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"730bdacb750351af356246366e83e9e6e30d9901","tid":1667301,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:26:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XWnUGbn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXWnUGbn.png&h=4b909146&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nbP4iYo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnbP4iYo.png&h=5fca0168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人就唔見<br />\n狗就見幾隻"},{"pid":"a4579c0d32bc3dff90b4a1c9830d508886cbb548","tid":1667301,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:27:20.000Z","msg":"人呢？去哂yoho？"},{"pid":"7cfc0563a39ed2bb73a2e3359e609dab10d0261d","tid":1667301,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:28:14.000Z","msg":"我就同啲狗你眼望我眼<br />\n人就唔見幾個"},{"pid":"9551f3fc3cc2f075f4b073cecde2bd5f8fc6d0bd","tid":1667301,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:28:56.000Z","msg":"啲狗都唔抖人架喎 同我玩眼望望"},{"pid":"937de2e0ca1794ee54c05b0a93425b5a91fc1cc2","tid":1667301,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:29:17.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"680bfa1e2c5687a24bc1bcc5bb9323ab58ff0e6a","tid":1667301,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:30:06.000Z","msg":"同啲狗玩心靈感應 幾好玩<br />\n有無多啲人黎？"},{"pid":"a1cde35c08a77e356e53c1e871cc8a9792cb3f46","tid":1667301,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:31:10.000Z","msg":"我已經想轉場落yoho<br />\n天西都無人既"},{"pid":"5dd5516569ed630f078235b0f71aa5cad7487d63","tid":1667301,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:31:59.000Z","msg":"有兩個蒙面Popo同我對望緊 我巧驚驚"},{"pid":"133d9cd5ed1cde0c1f181f72250ef41e93125b80","tid":1667301,"uid":38222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:32:59.000Z","msg":"小心便衣狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec75599d2b582542aa6570e7d8b23097c11176b0","tid":1667301,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"133d9cd5ed1cde0c1f181f72250ef41e93125b80","tid":1667301,"uid":38222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:32:59.000Z","msg":"小心便衣狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"我企咗係同一個位成十分鐘<br />\n啲popo又唔行過黎抖我<br />\n係到玩緊心靈感應"},{"pid":"ab38a1a2a928c65eb84a22210a9419aa80507ffb","tid":1667301,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:34:47.000Z","msg":"係一個口罩/黑衫都無喎大佬"},{"pid":"12299fe2957a8a7bb987c2ca348728c57816fc78","tid":1667301,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"680bfa1e2c5687a24bc1bcc5bb9323ab58ff0e6a","tid":1667301,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:30:06.000Z","msg":"同啲狗玩心靈感應 幾好玩<br />\n有無多啲人黎？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:35:07.000Z","msg":"辛苦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{